### GET ALL EMPLOYEES
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/leave-management/Employees
Content-Type: application/json

### CREATE USER EMPLOYEE
POST http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/leave-management/Employees
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "EmployeeID": "EMP1008",
  "Name": "Vishal",
  "Email": "vishal@test.com",
  "Department": "IT",
  "Role": "Employee"
}

### CREATE DUPLICATE EMPLOYEE
POST http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/leave-management/Employees
