### GET PENDING LEAVES
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/leave-management/getPendingLeaves()
Content-Type: application/json

### CREATE LEAVE REQUEST
POST http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/leave-management/LeaveRequests
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "LeaveID": "LV1008",
  "StartDate": "2026-06-20",
  "EndDate": "2026-06-22",
  "Reason": "Medical Leave",
  "AppliedOn": "2026-06-15",
  "employee_ID": "13829769-36c4-4e19-be07-07c72a37c609"
}

### CREATE LEAVE REQUEST WITH SAME LEAVEID
POST http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/leave-management/LeaveRequests
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "LeaveID": "LV1008",
  "StartDate": "2026-06-20",
  "EndDate": "2026-06-22",
  "Reason": "Medical Leave",
  "AppliedOn": "2026-06-15",
  "employee_ID": "13829769-36c4-4e19-be07-07c72a37c609"
}

