### UPDATE LEAVE REQUEST
PATCH http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/leave-management/LeaveRequests(2368209b-b2e1-466c-8c81-06779ef1409c)
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "Reason": "Updated medical leave reason"
}

### APPROVE LEAVE REQUEST
POST http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/leave-management/approveLeave
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "leaveID": "LV1006"
}

### APPROVE LEAVE REQUEST WITH INVALID ID
POST http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/leave-management/approveLeave
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "leaveID": "INVALID_ID"
}

### REJECT LEAVE REQUEST
POST http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/leave-management/rejectLeave
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "leaveID": "LV1007"
}

### REJECT LEAVE REQUEST WITH INVALID ID
POST http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/leave-management/rejectLeave
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "leaveID": "INVALID_ID"
}

### GET INDIVIDUAL EMPLOYEE LEAVES
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/leave-management/getEmployeeLeaves(employeeID='EMP1001')
Content-Type: application/json

### CHANGE LEAVE STATUS
POST http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/leave-management/changeLeaveStatus
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "leaveID": "LV1002",
  "status": "Rejected"
}